The '''Sir Rickard Christophers Medal''', named in honour of Sir [[Rickard Christophers]], is awarded every three years to individuals for their work in the field of tropical medicine and hygiene.<ref>{{cite web|title=Sir Rickard Christophers Medal|url=https://rstmh.org/awards/sir-rickard-christophers-medal|publisher=Royal Society of Tropical Medicine and Hygiene}}</ref> The awarding body is the [[Royal Society of Tropical Medicine and Hygiene]].
